  "returns": "Untrimmed spherical surface",
  "remarks": "The axis argument is the axis of the sphere; the refDir argument is perpendicular to the axis and through the center of the sphere and defines the origin of the UV space.\nYou can trim the resulting surface to generate a sheet body, for example, using\nISurface::CreateTrimmedSheet\n.",
